<title>USA: Harbinger Corp sets 3-for-2 stock split.</title>
<headline>Harbinger Corp sets 3-for-2 stock split.</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1997-01-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harbinger Corp said Friday that its board has declared a three-for-two stock split of its common shares, payable January 31 to shareholders of record January 17.</p>
<p>The total number of shares outstanding after the split will be about 18.9 million, the company said.</p>
